author: Anne Flaherty
title: When will the country get back to normal? 3 things to know about reopening America
description: Top health officials warn "we have not reached the peak."
content:
It's Easter weekend, and the nation's church pews aren't filled as President Donald Trump had hoped.
And while there are indications that social distancing is working as scientists had hoped in mitigating the spread of novel coronavirus, big questions remain… [+4601 chars]
